## Decision

The winner is **Refined Chain 01**, upgraded into the canonical form written in:
`/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/winning-chain.md`

