+
+## Constraints
+
+- Use only local repository materials.
+- Do not write full candidate definitions of `near-closed Tao circuit`.
+- Keep the distinction clear between:
+  - Tao's internal mechanism,
+  - exact-NS mismatch claims,
+  - and Step-1 scope-lock commitments.
+- If a feature remains undecided, classify it as `open but load-bearing` rather
+  than forcing a fake binary.
+
+## Deliverables
+
+Write:
