+1. `REPORT.md` containing:
+   - the packet/support semantics recommendation
+   - the conjugacy / helical / phase bookkeeping policy
+   - the canonicalization memo
+   - a cosmetic-vs-substantive change table
+   - a Step-2 inheritance verdict
